Increments/Decrement Operator

(++, --); It'll increment or decrement the value of variable by 1

++ : Increment Value of Variables by 1
-- : Decrement the value of variables by 1

Postfix Operator
    exp++;
     * Operators comes after the variable
     * first complete all other operations and then increment the value of varibale

 Prefix operator
    ++exp;
        * operators comes before variable
        * first increment the value of variable